00:00:00.250 --> 00:00:06.129
All transitions is tough and university
is no different, but there is help

00:00:06.129 --> 00:00:07.129
to help you get by.

00:00:07.129 --> 00:00:11.360
I just finished the first year
success program at Memorial University

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:14.880
and I'm looking to start my second year
in the next couple of months. First year

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:17.730
success is a program to help you

00:00:17.730 --> 00:00:22.769
adapt to university and get ready for the
workload and the environment

00:00:22.769 --> 00:00:25.390
that university presents.

00:00:25.390 --> 00:00:27.340
 

00:00:27.340 --> 00:00:30.190
 

